SUMMARY:Scotty McCreery Live in Concert
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $59 $79 $99 $109\nAMT Member Pre-Sale: Wednesday\, January 7 at 10:00 a.m.\nPublic On-Sale: Friday\, January 9 at 10:00 a.m. \nWith his warm baritone\, easy charm\, and authentic country roots\, Scotty McCreery has become one of today’s most beloved voices in country music. His chart-topping albums\, multi-platinum singles\, and heartfelt storytelling have earned him a devoted following and a standout place on the country music landscape. \nFans will hear favorites like “Five More Minutes\,” “Damn Strait\,” and “This Is It\,” along with the sincerity and energy that define Scotty’s live performances. His blend of tradition\, contemporary style\, and personal\, relatable lyrics creates a concert experience that resonates long after the last note. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
